nnaw_thumb-hf889d.jpg"></media:thumbnail><pubDate>Mon, 04 May 2026 21:25:52 GMT</pubDate><title>Anna Wintour arrives at the 2026 Met Gala</title><updateDate>Mon, 04 May 2026 22:56:24 GMT</updateDate></item><item><dateTimeWritten>Tue, 05 May 2026 13:18:53 GMT</dateTimeWritten><description>Blake Lively attended the Met Gala on Monday after reaching a settlement with former co-star and director Justin Baldoni, bringing an abrupt end to their year-long legal battle. Lively sued Baldoni and his production company for waging what she called a smear campaign against her after she accused him of sexual harassment on the set of their 2024 film “It Ends With Us,” which Baldoni consistently denied. NBC’s Laura Jarrett reports for TODAY.</description><expires>2056-05-05T12:31:58.000+0000</expires><guid isPermaLink="false">tdy_news_8a_jarrett_lively_baldoni_settlement_260505</guid><link>https://www.today.com/video/it-ends-with-a-deal-justin-baldoni-and-blake-lively-settle-lawsuit-262752837843</link><media:content url="https://prodamdnewsencoding.akamaized.net/NBC_News_Digital/tdy_news_8a_jarrett_lively_baldoni_settlement_260505/1/abs/index.m3u8" medium="video"><media:credit></media:credit><media:title>Blake Lively and Justin Baldoni Settle ‘It Ends With Us’ Legal Battle</media:title><media:player url="https://www.today.com/video/it-ends-with-a-deal-justin-baldoni-and-blake-lively-settle-lawsuit-262752837843"></media:player><media:thumbnail url="https://media-cldnry.s-nbcnews.com/image/upload/t_fit_1500w/mpx/2704722219/2026_05/1777984306135_tdy_news_8a_jarrett_lively_baldoni_settlement_260505_S3_1920x1080-te6gza.jpg"></media:thumbnail><media:description type="plain">Blake Lively attended the Met Gala on Monday after reaching a settlement with former co-star and director Justin Baldoni, bringing an abrupt end to their year-long legal battle. Lively sued Baldoni and his production company for waging what she called a smear campaign against her after she accused him of sexual harassment on the set of their 2024 film “It Ends With Us,” which Baldoni consistently denied. NBC’s Laura Jarrett reports for TODAY.</media:description><media:subTitle type="text/srt" lang="en-US" url="https://prodamdnewsencoding.akamaized.net/NBC_News_Digital/nbcnews/captions/2026/05/1777984306135_tdy_news_8a_jarrett_lively_baldoni_settlement_260505.srt"></media:subTitle><media:subTitle type="text/vtt" lang="en-US" url="https://prodamdnewsencoding.akamaized.net/NBC_News_Digital/nbcnews/captions/2026/05/1777984306135_tdy_news_8a_jarrett_lively_baldoni_settlement_260505.vtt"></media:subTitle></media:content><media:thumbnail url="https://media-cldnry.s-nbcnews.com/image/upload/t_fit_1500w/mpx/2704722219/2026_05/1777984306135_tdy_news_8a_jarrett_lively_baldoni_settlement_260505_S3_1920x1080-te6gza.jpg"></media:thumbnail><pubDate>Tue, 05 May 2026 12:31:52 GMT</pubDate><title>Blake Lively and Justin Baldoni Settle ‘It Ends With Us’ Legal Battle</title><updateDate>Tue, 05 May 2026 13:18:53 GMT</updateDate></item><item><dateTimeWritten>Tue, 05 May 2026 13:36:36 GMT</dateTimeWritten><description>Nearly 150 passengers, including 17 Americans, are trapped on a cruise ship off the coast of West Africa after seven possible cases of hantavirus have now been identified aboard, according to the World Health Organization. The suspected outbreak has killed at least three people and two other patients onboard the ship are being prepared for evacuation. NBC’s Camila Bernal reports for TODAY.</description><expires>2056-05-05T11:56:54.000+0000</expires><guid isPermaLink="false">tdy_news_7a_bernal_hantavirus_cruise_260505</guid><link>https://www.today.com/video/man-makes-emotional-plea-from-hantavirus-cruise-ship-262747205579</link><media:content url="https://prodamdnewsencoding.akamaized.net/NBC_News_Digital/tdy_news_7a_bernal_hantavirus_cruise_260505/1/abs/index.m3u8" medium="video"><media:credit></media:credit><media:title>Passenger Stuck on Cruise With Hantavirus Outbreak Speaks Out</media:title><media:player url="https://www.today.com/video/man-makes-emotional-plea-from-hantavirus-cruise-ship-262747205579"></media:player><media:thumbnail url="https://media-cldnry.s-nbcnews.com/image/upload/t_fit_1500w/mpx/2704722219/2026_05/1777982202681_tdy_news_7a_bernal_hantavirus_cruise_260505_S3_1920x1080-e9byye.jpg"></media:thumbnail><media:description type="plain">Nearly 150 passengers, including 17 Americans, are trapped on a cruise ship off the coast of West Africa after seven possible cases of hantavirus have now been identified aboard, according to the World Health Organization. The suspected outbreak has killed at least three people and two other patients onboard the ship are being prepared for evacuation. NBC’s Camila Bernal reports for TODAY.</media:description><media:subTitle type="text/srt" lang="en-US" url="https://prodamdnewsencoding.akamaized.net/NBC_News_Digital/nbcnews/captions/2026/05/1777982202681_tdy_news_7a_bernal_hantavirus_cruise_260505.srt"></media:subTitle><media:subTitle type="text/vtt" lang="en-US" url="https://prodamdnewsencoding.akamaized.net/NBC_News_Digital/nbcnews/captions/2026/05/1777982202681_tdy_news_7a_bernal_hantavirus_cruise_260505.vtt"></media:subTitle></media:content><media:thumbnail url="https://media-cldnry.s-nbcnews.com/image/upload/t_fit_1500w/mpx/2704722219/2026_05/1777982202681_tdy_news_7a_bernal_hantavirus_cruise_260505_S3_1920x1080-e9byye.jpg"></media:thumbnail><pubDate>Tue, 05 May 2026 11:56:49 GMT</pubDate><title>Passenger Stuck on Cruise With Hantavirus Outbreak Speaks Out</title><updateDate>Tue, 05 May 2026 13:36:36 GMT</updateDate></item><item><dc:creator>Corky Siemaszko</dc:creator><dateTimeWritten>Mon, 04 May 2026 17:00:36 GMT</dateTimeWritten><description>Spirit Airlines said in court papers filed Monday that it was forced to ground its fleet for good over the weekend because &#34;recent geopolitical events resulted in a massive and sustained increase in fuel prices.&#34;While the court papers did not specify the nature of those geopolitical events, jet fuel prices have soared in the two months since the start of the war in Iran.&#34;The Debtors and their advisors searched for increased capital and any sources of savings or liquidity, leaving no option unexp</description><expires>2112-01-01T00:00:00.000+0000</expires><guid>https://www.nbcnews.com/business/travel/spirit-airlines-doomed-sky-high-fuel-prices-due-recent-geopolitical-ev-rcna343466</guid><link>https://www.nbcnews.com/business/travel/spirit-airlines-doomed-sky-high-fuel-prices-due-recent-geopolitical-ev-rcna343466</link><media:content url="https://media-cldnry.s-nbcnews.com/image/upload/t_fit_1500w/rockcms/2026-05/260504-spirit-airlines-ew-1126a-8debc2.jpg" type="image/jpeg" medium="image" height="1667" width="2500"><media:credit>Giorgio Viera</media:credit><media:text type="plain">Spirit Airlines</media:text><media:description type="plain">Spirit Airlines jets sit on the tarmac as the company ceased operations at Fort Lauderdale-Hollywood International Airport in Fort Lauderdale, Fla., on May 2, 2026. </media:description></media:content><media:thumbnail url="https://media-cldnry.s-nbcnews.com/image/upload/t_fit_1500w/rockcms/2026-05/260504-spirit-airlines-ew-1126a-8debc2.jpg" height="1667" width="2500"></media:thumbnail><pubDate>Mon, 04 May 2026 17:00:36 GMT</pubDate><title>Spirit Airlines doomed by high fuel prices due to &#39;recent geopolitical events,&#39; court docs state</title><updateDate>Mon, 04 May 2026 17:00:36 GMT</updateDate></item></channel></rss>